WEBVTT


00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.160
I was born in the 1900s

00:00:02.161 --> 00:00:06.400
so I might be a little old fashioned in the sense that I like to cook

00:00:06.401 --> 00:00:08.680
clean and satisfy my husband's needs

00:00:08.681 --> 00:00:09.800
there's nothing wrong with that

00:00:09.801 --> 00:00:10.760
some of y'all look

00:00:10.761 --> 00:00:13.420
people like to tell me otherwise

00:00:13.480 --> 00:00:16.520
or unhappy women who have been scorned by men

00:00:16.521 --> 00:00:18.800
and want to burn the whole world down

00:00:18.801 --> 00:00:20.480
I'm happy exactly how I am

00:00:20.481 --> 00:00:23.320
so is my husband so words of advice

00:00:23.321 --> 00:00:24.779
do whatever makes you happy
